      • MM_MarketTradingStatus

        static final int MM_MarketTradingStatus
        This is the tag used to store trading status. (Note that it matches the standard FIX tag value).

        It should have one of the above TRADINGSTATUS_ values.

        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • MM_MarketIDCode

        static final int MM_MarketIDCode
        Tag used to store the market identifier.

        The codes used will depend on the market info implementation. For example, FIX versions up to 4.2 used the Reuters exchange mnemonics. FIX versions 4.3 and later use the ISO 10383 Market Identifier Code's.

        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
